  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-1-1681817865622-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-1-1681817865622-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-1-1681817865622-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-1-1681817865622-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-1-1681817865622-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely, separating the white and green parts</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> mangetout </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Slice your <strong>chestnut mushrooms </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-2-1681817869034-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-2-1681817869034-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-2-1681817869034-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-2-1681817869034-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-2-1681817869034-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>star anise</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min, stirring constantly, or until fragrant and sizzling</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>diced chicken</strong> <strong>breast </strong>and <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until lightly browned</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-3-1681817872889-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-3-1681817872889-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-3-1681817872889-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-3-1681817872889-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-3-1681817872889-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong> and<strong> rice vinegar</strong> to the pot and cook for 30 secs or until evaporated</p><p>Add 1L <span class=\"text-purple\">[1.5L]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, sprinkle in your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and whisk thoroughly to combine</p><p>Bring to the boil and once boiling, reduce the heat to medium</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-4-1681817876048-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-4-1681817876048-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-4-1681817876048-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-4-1681817876048-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-4-1681817876048-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>wholewheat</strong> <strong>noodles</strong> to the pot and cook for 4-5 min, or until nearly cooked but with a slight bite</p><p>Tip: The noodles will carry on cooking, so aim for 'al dente' at this point!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-5-1681817879688-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-5-1681817879688-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-5-1681817879688-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-5-1681817879688-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-5-1681817879688-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> <strong>whites</strong> (you'll use the greens later!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-6-1681817883642-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-6-1681817883642-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-6-1681817883642-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-6-1681817883642-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-6-1681817883642-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>mangetout </strong>and cook for a final 2 min or until the noodles are tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>warming</strong> <strong>chicken & ginger ramen</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-7-1681817886683-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-7-1681817886683-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-7-1681817886683-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-7-1681817886683-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Copy-of-Step-7-1681817886683-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>warming chicken & ginger ramen</strong> in bowls</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion greens</strong> and discard the star anise</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
